# Frontend prototype traceability

- Identify affected Pxx and Pxx-A4-xx references before editing.
- Reuse the existing design system and shared components.
- Match approved hierarchy, actions, content states, privacy wording and responsive intent.
- Do not add decorative controls without functional destinations.
- Do not display scanner, quarantine, verification, audit or integration status without an evidence-backed backend contract.
- Cover relevant P46 empty/loading/error/success states.
- Preserve accessibility: semantic structure, keyboard access, visible focus, validation and useful errors.
- Add or update frontend tests and browser smoke evidence.
